—ظSarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/commands/docs/stor_create.mdظ@82b4567c3d1de89996a88a42e66044fe43ff6fdd55af61e3f06db4c5ce8719ef²title: stor create‘¨ExamplesعœCreate an in-memory sqlite database with specified table name, column names, and column data types
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> stor create --table-name nudb --columns {bool1: bool, int1: int, float1: float, str1: str, datetime1: datetime}


```
Create an in-memory sqlite database with a json column
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> stor create --table-name files_with_md --columns {file: str, metadata: jsonb}


```
’گگعخTitle: title: stor create
Path: Examples
Content:
Create an in-memory sqlite database with specified table name, column names, and column data types
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> stor create --table-name nudb --columns {bool1: bool, int1: int, float1: float, str1: str, datetime1: datetime}


```
Create an in-memory sqlite database with a json column
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> stor create --table-name files_with_md --columns {file: str, metadata: jsonb}


```
